edu.smcm.ai.sliding_block

Class OutOfPlace

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.smcm.ai.search.Heuristic
      • edu.smcm.ai.sliding_block.OutOfPlace

  • public class OutOfPlace
extends Heuristic
    A heuristic that simply counts the number of tiles that are not in their correct place in the puzzle. See page Russell and Norvig, Artificial Intelligence: A Modern Approach, Third Edition, p. 103.
